data.description: Fantastic Opportunity!!! This classic and inviting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom traditional home exudes timeless charm and comfort. Nestled in Liberty Pointe, this residence features a spacious living area perfect for gatherings, a cozy kitchen equipped with modern appliances, and a private backyard oasis ideal for relaxation. With four well-appointed bedrooms offering ample space and three bathrooms for added convenience, this home provides a perfect blend of functionality and traditional elegance for comfortable living. Hurry and Bring Your Offers!!! This home wont last long!!!
